page.title: 11WOOKEY HOLE CAVES.
page.content: THE RIVER AXE FLOWS THROUGH WOOKEY HOLE CAVES AND BY THE VILLAGE CAR PARK. THERE IT IS, FLOWING OVER LOTS OF STONES,AND SOME WEEDS, BUT NOT MANY FLOWERS.IN THE STREAM THERE ISN'T MUCH WILDLIFE TO BE SEEN BECAUSE IT WOULD PROBABLY BE HIDING IN THE WEED. IT IS NICE AND PEACEFUL TO JUST SIT BY THE RIVER AND LISTEN TO THE RUNNING WATER. LOCAL BOYS ENJOY FISHING IN THE RIVER, BY THE CAR PARK OR AT TROUT'S BEND WHERE THE RIVER GENTLY WANDERS ALONG WITH DEEPS AND SHALLOWS, LINED BY TREES AND ECHOING THE SOUNDS OF THE BIRDS. ON AND ON, GOES THE RIVER, PAST FIELDS AND HEDGES,GRAZING CATTLE AND THE PEACEFUL SOMERSET COUNTRYSIDE.
